  "title": "Clinical Nurse / Private Nursing",
  "description": "<p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Conduct home visits and nursing assessment</li><li>Perform nursing procedures and assessment.</li><li>Triage clinical conditions and respond in a timely manner.</li><li>Develop and implement patient care plans as part of a team.</li><li>Manage and monitor a patient's needs.</li><li>ADLs</li><li>Maintain proper documentation.</li><li>Assisting the Doctor as needed.</li><li>Provide Caregiver Training.</li><li>Provide Private Shift Nursing at Home</li><li>Conduct peritoneal dialysis training in hospitals and at home.</li><li>Call centre manning.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Candidates are required to travel to the relevant locations as needed.</li><li>Diploma or degree in Nursing.</li><li>At least 1 - 2 years working experience in acute hospitals.</li><li>Registered with Singapore Nursing Board.</li><li>Prior experience with dialysis machine operation is a bonus, but not necessary.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Terms:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Remuneration: $3000 onwards with transport allowances.</li><li>Training will be provided.</li><li>44 hours work week.</li><li>13th Month</li></ul>",
